<doc>
  <member name="D3D12_VIDEO_MOTION_ESTIMATOR_SEARCH_BLOCK_SIZE_FLAGS">
    <summary>
      <para>Specifies the motion estimation search block sizes that a video encoder supports.</para>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>Query for supported block sizes by calling <see cref="ID3D12VideoDevice.CheckFeatureSupport" /> and specifying the feature value of <see cref="D3D12_FEATURE_VIDEO_MOTION_ESTIMATOR" />.</para>
    </remarks>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_VIDEO_MOTION_ESTIMATOR_SEARCH_BLOCK_SIZE_FLAGS.D3D12_VIDEO_MOTION_ESTIMATOR_SEARCH_BLOCK_SIZE_FLAG_NONE">
    <summary>
      <para>Search block size is not supported by the encoder.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_VIDEO_MOTION_ESTIMATOR_SEARCH_BLOCK_SIZE_FLAGS.D3D12_VIDEO_MOTION_ESTIMATOR_SEARCH_BLOCK_SIZE_FLAG_8X8">
    <summary>
      <para>The encoder supports a search block size of 8x8 pixels.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_VIDEO_MOTION_ESTIMATOR_SEARCH_BLOCK_SIZE_FLAGS.D3D12_VIDEO_MOTION_ESTIMATOR_SEARCH_BLOCK_SIZE_FLAG_16X16">
    <summary>
      <para>The encoder supports a search block size of 16x16 pixels.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
</doc>